00:43:13.126 --> 00:43:15.686
electron at some place is not
the same as the probability of

00:43:15.686 --> 00:43:17.510
finding them with exchanged
positions.

00:43:17.510 --> 00:43:20.291
For example,
the chance of finding the

00:43:20.291 --> 00:43:24.880
